# === kernel & firmware =======================================================
# linux-firmware is the meta-package: it pulls in ALL sub-packages including
# i915, amdgpu, rtw88, iwlwifi, etc.  Don't add the sub-packages directly —
# their standalone names change between Alpine versions.
linux-lts
linux-firmware
mkinitfs

